</p><p><span>I=E2=80=99ve spent the past few months tinkering with a script=
 for a video essay with a </span><em>Times</em><span> editor. We finally fi=
nished and filmed in New York a couple weeks ago. Some will wonder why I=E2=
=80=99m choosing to work with them after they </span><a href=3D"https://www=
.robkhenderson.com/p/troubled-is-a-national-bestsellerbut" rel=3D"">left my=
