k-times-bestseller-list-politically-biased" rel=3D"">coverage of what trans=
pired</a><span>). Main reasons: This is a chance to reach people who should=
 hear about the luxury beliefs concept (NYT readers), it will lead more peo=
ple to read </span><em><a href=3D"https://www.amazon.com/Troubled-Memoir-Fo=
ster-Family-Social/dp/1982168536/ref=3Dtmm_hrd_swatch_0?_encoding=3DUTF8&am=
p;qid=3D1687225601&amp;sr=3D8-2-fkmr2" rel=3D"">Troubled</a></em><span> and=
 grasp the deeper point I=E2=80=99m making, and the staff who work in opini=
on are separate from those who manage the list. As Erik Hoel </span><a href=
=3D"https://www.theintrinsicperspective.com/p/how-the-new-york-times-beat-m=
e" rel=3D"">says</a><span>, the house always wins. </span></p><p><span>Link=
